7:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd3512fe8f2bd82bd5ea8444d1a9cd368cf7df2","tid":2510406,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"警方前年11月初在灣仔堅拿道西一個單位內撿獲近140支汽油彈或半製成品。年齡介乎19至24歲的四男一女被控以管有爆炸品罪，控罪及後修訂為串謀縱火罪，為反修例運動已知案件中，撿取最多汽油彈及半製成品的案件。其中23歲女被告早前在區域法院承認交替的管有物品意圖摧毀或損毀財產罪，法官葉佐文今判她入獄38個月。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，案發當天維園有集會進行，警方刑事情報科人員監視堅拿道西冠景樓4樓一個單位，同日下午採取行動。兩名警員掩至單位門外，察覺單位傳出濃烈汽油味，其中一名警員表露身份，要求單位內人士開門不果，遂破門而入。<br />\n<br />\n惟警員進入後發現單位無人，同時獲同袍從通訊機通知，單位內有四男一女由露台位置跳到3樓簷蓬，再由簷蓬跳到3樓平台逃走。5人逃走時遭一名不知名人士拍下過程，而片段中5人均沒有蒙面，面容清晰可見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/IWG7MB4QGRBP3MTFDXZHPSSNIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FIWG7MB4QGRBP3MTFDXZHPSSNIM%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=6114ea83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FIWG7MB4QGRBP3MTFDXZHPSSNIM%2F&h=930ee031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/IWG7MB4QGRBP3MTFDXZHPSSNIM/</a>"},{"pid":"0dfa2414783108166216ac225db48f0fbadc9bef","tid":2510406,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20e963aa9fe4fdcc8a182f7b7f155041655ca30","tid":2510406,"uid":15697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efb485d3df7e53bb5596cc69a6f2577bc99d5770","tid":2510406,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ec1b0dbb46c8479b2b4a6ef77710a875f9c77c7e","tid":2510406,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"還押逾17個月可以扣幾多刑期?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"